      "orig": "Note thatthisconventionfortheDFTmeans thatthe area under a function squared is not the same as the area under its transform squared-a factor Nmust be includedin theParseval-Rayleighformula.Alternate conventionscould have a l/\u221aNon both sides or the 1/Non the other side.Thisconventionmakes the forward transform ofaunit impulseequal toaconstant spectrum of one,analogous to the continuous case.",
      "text": "Note thatthisconventionfortheDFTmeans thatthe area under a function squared is not the same as the area under its transform squared-a factor Nmust be includedin theParseval-Rayleighformula.Alternate conventionscould have a l/\u221aNon both sides or the 1/Non the other side.Thisconventionmakes the forward transform ofaunit impulseequal toaconstant spectrum of one,analogous to the continuous case."
